                            </div>
                            <span class="tweet-author">
                             <a href="//twitter.com/HarvardWCFIA" target="_blank">
                              HarvardWCFIA
                             </a>
                            </span>
                            <span class="tweet-text">
                             When Life Is in Limbo, Education Can't Wait | Associate Professor of Education
                             <a href="http://twitter.com/drydenpeterson" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="@drydenpeterson">
                              @drydenpeterson
                             </a>
                             shares insights from her team’s work on refugee education around the world
                             <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23IWD2019" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="#IWD2019">
